PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS providing that tax credits for a taxpayer under The Manitoba Employee Ownership Fund Corporation Act, or the Labour Sponsored Venture Capital Corporations Act, 1992 (Ontario) will not be included in a taxpayers's income or reduce the cost to the taxpayer of the share.
